Dialogues.Line: The old days of magic are long gone, but I’ll be damned if I let that stop me.
This machine is more temperamental than any spell I’ve ever cast!

[2024-12-06 10:10] Now, I'd rather be winding down at the bakery right now, getting a thick slice of that fresh bread, but this challenge is too interesting to pass up. Magic may be a thing of the past, Kai, but let's see if we can add some magic of our own to these new era machines, eh?
